Package powerwalk.control

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mapper
    This class collects data from the RSBot environment and stores it in the singleton WorldMap-object

    Noticeboard
    This class handles interaction with the Noticeboard, such as opening and closing the Noticeboard and opening a specific Tab.
    Noticeboard.Tab
    This class represents a Tab of the Noticeboard.
    PathFinder
    This Utility class deals with finding a path between two Points in the RSBot environment.
    WidgetManager
    Manages opening of Widgets in order to access the various possibilities that the RSBot environment provides.
    XMLToolBox
    Utility class providing methods for handling XML files
